Tesseract.js v7.0.0 Assets
==========================

These files are used for offline OCR processing in the browser extension.
They are kept locally to comply with Content Security Policy (CSP) and ensure 100% privacy/offline capability.

Source URLs (v7.0.0):
- worker.min.js: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js@7.0.0/dist/worker.min.js
- tesseract-core-simd-lstm.wasm.js: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js-core@7.0.0/tesseract-core-simd-lstm.wasm.js
- tesseract-core-simd-lstm.wasm: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js-core@7.0.0/tesseract-core-simd-lstm.wasm
- tesseract-core-relaxedsimd-lstm.wasm.js: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js-core@7.0.0/tesseract-core-relaxedsimd-lstm.wasm.js
- tesseract-core-relaxedsimd-lstm.wasm: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js-core@7.0.0/tesseract-core-relaxedsimd-lstm.wasm
- tesseract-core-lstm.wasm.js: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js-core@7.0.0/tesseract-core-lstm.wasm.js
- tesseract-core-lstm.wasm: https://unpkg.com/tesseract.js-core@7.0.0/tesseract-core-lstm.wasm

Note:
`tesseract.min.js` is NOT included here as it is bundled directly from `node_modules` in the build process.
Only the worker and WASM cores are loaded at runtime from this directory.
